@personal_assistant_api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5082
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_FROM_LOGIN

GET {{personal_assistant_api_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

### Technology Mastery — create technology
POST {{personal_assistant_api_HostAddress}}/api/technologies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "name": "Kubernetes", "color": "#326ce5", "icon": "tabler:brand-docker", "notes": "" }

###

### List technologies (verify computed scoring fields)
GET {{personal_assistant_api_HostAddress}}/api/technologies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Add a practice section (subtítulo)
POST {{personal_assistant_api_HostAddress}}/api/technologies/1/practice-sections
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "title": "1. Fundamentos" }

###

### Add practice item (sectionId from the section created above)
POST {{personal_assistant_api_HostAddress}}/api/technologies/1/practice-items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "sectionId": 1, "title": "Crear un Deployment", "points": 2 }

###

### Mark practice item done with a bitácora note
PUT {{personal_assistant_api_HostAddress}}/api/technologies/1/practice-items/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "isDone": true, "notes": "Desplegué nginx con 3 réplicas en minikube" }

###

### Add a theory section (subtítulo)
POST {{personal_assistant_api_HostAddress}}/api/technologies/1/theory-sections
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "title": "Fundamentos" }

###

### Add theory question (sectionId from the section created above)
POST {{personal_assistant_api_HostAddress}}/api/technologies/1/theory-questions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "sectionId": 1, "question": "¿Qué es un Pod?", "points": 5 }

###

### Mark theory question mastered
PUT {{personal_assistant_api_HostAddress}}/api/technologies/1/theory-questions/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{ "isMastered": true, "notes": "" }

###

### Re-fetch technology — confirm totalScore/level reflect both toggles proportionally
GET {{personal_assistant_api_HostAddress}}/api/technologies/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Import topics from CSV (Category,Subcategory,Name,Type,Points)
### Creates/reuses practice-sections and theory-sections by Subcategory name (col 2, e.g. "Fundamentos"),
### stores Category (col 1) as an informative field on each topic, skips duplicates
### (same Subcategory+Name), and preserves row order via the Order field.
POST {{personal_assistant_api_HostAddress}}/api/technologies/1/import-csv
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "csv": "Practice,Fundamentos,Instalar Minikube o Kind,Practice,5\nPractice,Fundamentos,Instalar kubectl,Practice,3\nPractice,Networking,Configurar Ingress,Practice,20\nTheory,Arquitectura,¿Qué es Kubernetes?,Theory,5"
}

###
